Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:15.47,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.11,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.11,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:22.64,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:22.64,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
